<br>
I consider the skald's role to be more about melee than support, given that this IS Midgard, after all. And I envision the skalds literally bellowing throughout a battle, urging their consorts to greater feats of valor and putting fear in the hearts of the Enemy!<br>
<br>
That said: wouldn't it be great, AND make sense, to give the skald a short-range PBAOE Mezz? <br>
<br>
The skald throws out a mighty curse about how his companions are gunna tear off the opposing side's limbs, and whammo - the enemy pack freezes in fear for a good 10 seconds. <br>
<br>
What think ye?  Would help in keep defense, too!<br>
